OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FWater bosses could face up to two
OL,7,Fyears in jail under new government
OL,8,Fplans to crack down on water companies
OL,9,Fthat damage the environment.
OL,11,FUnder previous laws, the maximum
OL,12,Fpunishment for polluting was a fine,
OL,13,Fbut new legislation being put before
OL,14,FParliament on Wednesday could see
OL,15,Fwater bosses face jail time.
OL,17,FThe plans will hand new powers to
OL,18,Fwater regulators, make it easier for
OL,19,Fcompanies to be fined, and also ban
OL,20,Fbonuses for water bosses if they fail
OL,21,Fto meet high standards.
