OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,7,F"After years of neglect, our waterways
OL,8,Fare now in an unacceptable state.
OL,10,F"Under this government, water
OL,11,Fexecutives will no longer line their
OL,12,Fown pockets whilst pumping out this
OL,13,Ffilth. If they refuse to comply, they
OL,14,Fcould end up in the dock and face
OL,15,Fprison time.
OL,17,F"The public are furious that in 21st
OL,18,Fcentury Britain, record levels of
OL,19,Fsewage are being pumped into our
OL,20,Frivers, lakes and seas", he said.
