OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FIn a speech at Thames Rowing Club in
OL,7,FPutney, Reed said the former
OL,8,FConservative government was "too weak"
OL,9,Fto stop water companies paying out
OL,10,Fmillions in bonuses and dividends at
OL,11,Fthe expense of infrastructure upgrades.
OL,13,F"While I can't undo the failure of the
OL,14,Fpast, I can stop it ever happening
OL,15,Fagain. We've inherited a broken water
OL,16,Fsystem that affects us all, from the
OL,17,Fhealth and happiness of communities to
OL,18,Fthe quality and resilience of our food
OL,19,Fsystems and natural environment", Reed
OL,20,Ftold stakeholders.
