OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FThe government say the current system
OL,7,Ffails to hold firms accountable for
OL,8,Fwidespread illegal polluting in the
OL,9,Fsector.
OL,11,FEnvironmental activist and singer
OL,12,FFeargal Sharkey criticised the
OL,13,Fgovernment's plans, telling Sky News
OL,14,Fhe didn't believe anyone would ever be
OL,15,Fjailed under the proposed laws.
OL,17,F"I guarantee you right now it will
OL,18,Fnever ever happen; what we needed was
OL,19,Fdecisive clear leadership and sadly I
OL,20,Fcan't see that today", he said.
