OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FMr Sharkey also said that rather than
OL,7,Fintroducing new laws, the government
OL,8,Fneeded to better enforce the
OL,9,Flegislation already in place.
OL,11,F"We don't need new regulations, we
OL,12,Fdon't need new laws, we've got 35
OL,13,Fyears' worth of laws that have never
OL,14,Fbeen applied ` you should force them
OL,15,Fto go out and apply the law as it
OL,16,Fstands today, that would have been a
OL,17,Fmassive step forward", he said.
