OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FThe quality of England's rivers, lakes
OL,7,Fand seas has plummeted in recent years
OL,8,Fas the number of sewage spills has
OL,9,Fincreased.
OL,11,FCurrently, no single river in England
OL,12,Fis considered to be in good overall
OL,13,Fhealth, and beauty spots including
OL,14,FWindermere in the Lake District have
OL,15,Fbeen polluted.
OL,17,FSome water utilities are also creaking
OL,18,Funder high levels of debt or face
OL,19,Fcriticism over dividends to
OL,20,Fshareholders and executive bonuses.
