OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FThames Water has just announced that
OL,7,Fit will need to hike customer bills by
OL,8,Fnearly 60% by 2030, warning that any
OL,9,Fother action will leave it
OL,10,F"uninvestible".
OL,12,FThis in turn has led to water
OL,13,Fcompanies requesting permission to
OL,14,Fsharply increase bills to address the
OL,15,Fconcerns.
OL,17,FUnder the proposed laws, regulators
OL,18,Fwill be able to issue severe and
OL,19,Fautomatic fines without having to
OL,20,Fdirect resources to lengthy
OL,21,Finvestigations, the government said.
