OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FCurrently, the regulators cannot
OL,7,Fimpose fixed financial penalties for
OL,8,Fmost offences and the current maximum
OL,9,Ffine is just #300, meaning it is not
OL,10,Fcost effective for them to penalise
OL,11,Ffrequent, more minor offences.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
