OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FCurrently, some 14,000 storm overflows
OL,7,Facross England are monitored so that
OL,8,Fany discharge of untreated sewage
OL,9,Fduring periods of heavy rain can be
OL,10,Freported.
OL,12,FHowever, water firms will now be
OL,13,Frequired to fully monitor the 7,000
OL,14,Femergency overflows, which are only
OL,15,Fpermitted to discharge raw sewage as a
OL,16,Flast resort from the network in the
OL,17,Fevent of issues such as power outages
OL,18,For pump failures.
