OL,6,FThe firms will then be required to
OL,7,Fpublish real-time data for all
OL,8,Femergency overflows to ensure
OL,9,Ftransparency and alert the public.
OL,11,FTo ensure regulators are properly
OL,12,Ffunded, the bill will expand powers
OL,13,Ffor the watchdogs to recover costs
OL,14,Ffrom water companies for enforcement
OL,15,Faction taken in response to their
OL,16,Ffailings.
