OL,3,CWater bosses could face two years in
OL,4,Cjail for sewage dumping
OL,6,FOfwat will also be required to set
OL,7,Frules that ensure companies appoint
OL,8,Fdirectors and chief executives, and
OL,9,Fallow them to remain in post, only
OL,10,Fwhen they meet the highest standards
OL,11,Fof "fitness and propriety".
OL,13,FElsewhere, there will be a new
OL,14,Fstatutory requirement for water
OL,15,Fcompanies to publish annual pollution
OL,16,Fincident reduction plans that outline
OL,17,Fthe steps they are taking to address
OL,18,Fpollution incidents.
